    <div style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-soft);margin-bottom:8px">Stai per eliminare <strong id="del_client_name" style="color:var(--white)"></strong>.</div>
    <div style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:18px">Le foto occupano spazio in localStorage. Vuoi mantenerle o eliminarle definitivamente?</div>
    <div id="del_foto_info" style="background:rgba(244,196,48,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(244,196,48,0.2);padding:10px 13px;margin-bottom:16px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--yellow)"></div>
